### ============================================
### Test Routes Through Gateway
### ============================================

### Get Customers (via Gateway → Customer Service)
GET http://localhost:4004/api/customers
Accept: application/json

### Get Customer by ID (via Gateway → Customer Service)
GET http://localhost:4004/api/customers/{{customerId}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Accounts (via Gateway → Account Service)
GET http://localhost:4004/api/accounts
Accept: application/json

### Get Account by ID (via Gateway → Account Service)
GET http://localhost:4004/api/accounts/{{accountId}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Transactions (via Gateway → Transaction Service)
GET http://localhost:4004/api/transactions
Accept: application/json

### Get Transaction by ID (via Gateway → Transaction Service)
GET http://localhost:4004/api/transactions/{{transactionId}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Payments (via Gateway → Payment Service)
GET http://localhost:4004/api/payments
Accept: application/json

### Create Payment (via Gateway → Payment Service)
POST http://localhost:4004/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceAccountId": "{{sourceAccountId}}",
  "destinationAccountId": "{{destinationAccountId}}",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Test payment via gateway"
}
